---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HandDrawnDivider from '../../components/HandDrawnDivider';
---

<Layout title="About | Zhong Pengchen">
  <main class="w-full min-h-screen max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 relative">
    
    <!-- Back / Door icon -->
    <a href="/" class="group absolute top-8 left-0 md:-left-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition-transform hover:-translate-x-2 z-10">
      <div class="w-8 h-12 border-2 border-ink-main border-b-0 relative bg-bg-paper">
        <div class="absolute right-1 top-1/2 w-1 h-1 bg-ink-main rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <span class="font-[Caveat] text-lg text-ink-muted mt-1 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">Return</span>
    </a>

    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-wide mb-4">About Me / 关于我</h1>
      <p class="font-[Caveat] text-2xl text-ink-muted">A brief introduction.</p>
    </header>

    <HandDrawnDivider client:load />

    <article class="prose prose-lg mt-12 w-full max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Zhong Pengchen</strong>. I am a researcher and designer interested in the intersection of human-computer interaction, spatial interfaces, and minimalist web design.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        你好，我是钟鹏晨。我相信个人网站应该是非常私人化的表达，而不是使用千篇一律的标准化模板。这也是为什么我用手绘元素（Rough.js）和空间隐喻（门与楼梯）来构建这个属于我的空间。
      </p>

      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <ul class="list-none pl-0">
        <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-mono text-ink-muted mr-4">2025 - 现今</span> <strong>Independent Researcher</strong> (独立研究员)</li>
        <li class="mb-2"><span class="font-mono text-ink-muted mr-4">2022 - 2025</span> <strong>Frontend Engineer</strong> (前端开发)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        You can reach me via email at <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a> or find me on <a href="#">Twitter</a> and <a href="#">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-20 mb-8">
        <HandDrawnDivider client:load />
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a href="/" class="font-[Caveat] text-2xl text-ink-muted hover:text-ink-main transition-colors">Return to the stairs</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </main>
</Layout>
